{title: A Letter To My Heart}
{artist: Jim Reeves}
{composer: written by Cindy Walker}

[G]Dear heart there is [D7]something I must [G]tell you
Something [D7]sad and so hard for me to [G]say
For I [C]know how much you always [G]loved her
And how you [D7]always hoped that she'd come back [G]someday

But day after [D7]day my hopes grow [G]dimmer
As I [D7]watched life and love passing me [G]by
And the [C]life I live is empty and so [G]lonely
